	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=17061&amp;start=45">What's the reason for the missing PPU cycle on even frames?</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320">Moderators</a></p>

</div>

